    "We tune λ ∈ {10 -3, 5 × 10 -3 } for PoLAR and set α = 32.",
    "We choose the combination that performs best on average throughout all datasets (see Table 10) and report these.",
    "For the comparison in Table 1, we train again on each task for 5 epochs with η = 4 × 10 -3 and set λ = 0.1 for all datasets and settings.",
